---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms and Condition | Hyperperformance Media"
  description="Terms and conditions for using the Hyperperformance Media website and engaging our digital marketing services."
  path="/terms"
>
  <section class="bg-background px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-h2 text-text-primary" data-reveal>Terms and Condition</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-body-sm text-text-secondary" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            By accessing and using the Hyperperformance Media website, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website or services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Hyperperformance Media provides digital marketing services including but not limited to SEO, website development, social media management, performance marketing, and content creation. Specific deliverables, timelines, and pricing for any engagement will be outlined in a separate service agreement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            All content on this website — including text, graphics, logos, images, and design elements — is the property of Hyperperformance Media unless otherwise stated. Upon full payment, client-owned deliverables (websites, content, designs) will be transferred to the client as outlined in the service agreement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">4. Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Clients are responsible for providing accurate information, timely feedback, and necessary access to platforms and accounts required for service delivery. Delays caused by client-side factors may affect project timelines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">5. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Payment schedules and methods will be specified in the service agreement. Unless otherwise agreed, invoices are due within 15 days of issuance. Late payments may result in paused work until the outstanding balance is settled.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Hyperperformance Media is not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. While we strive for excellent results, we do not guarantee specific rankings, traffic figures, or revenue outcomes, as these depend on factors beyond our control.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">7. Termination</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Either party may terminate a service engagement with 30 days written notice. Fees for work completed up to the termination date are non-refundable. Pre-paid amounts for unstarted work will be refunded on a pro-rata basis.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-h4 text-text-primary">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            For questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@hyperformancemedia.in" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">info@hyperformancemedia.in</a> or +91-9643534849.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
